---
---

<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-headline">
  <div class="hero__inner coach-section-inner">

    <div class="hero__content">

      <p class="hero__eyebrow eyebrow" >
        Executive Coach · Αθήνα · ICF-PCC
      </p>

      <h1 class="hero__name" id="hero-headline">
        Νίκος<br />Σπυρόπουλος
      </h1>

      <p class="hero__statement">
        Βοηθώ executives να βγουν από θέσεις<br class="hero__br" />
        που δεν τους χωράνε πλέον.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__metrics" aria-label="Εμπειρία και στοιχεία">
        <div class="hero__metric">
          <span class="hero__metric-num">12</span>
          <span class="hero__metric-label eyebrow">χρόνια corporate<br />leadership</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__metric">
          <span class="hero__metric-num">30+</span>
          <span class="hero__metric-label eyebrow">professionals<br />coached σε transition</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__metric">
          <span class="hero__metric-num">ICF</span>
          <span class="hero__metric-label eyebrow">PCC certified<br />coach</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="hero__cta hero__cta--primary">
          <span>Δωρεάν discovery call</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 10h12M11 5l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#packages" class="hero__cta hero__cta--ghost">Δες τα πακέτα</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--c-bg);
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: var(--s-9) var(--s-7);
  }
  .hero__inner { width: 100%; }

  .hero__content {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--s-6);
    max-width: 52rem;
  }

  .hero__eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--s-3);
  }
  .hero__eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--c-amber);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero__name {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--c-ink);
  }

  .hero__statement {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--c-ink-2);
    max-width: 42ch;
  }
  .hero__br { display: none; }
  @media (min-width: 640px) { .hero__br { display: block; } }

  .hero__metrics {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--s-7);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-block: var(--s-5);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }
  .hero__metric { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s-1); }
  .hero__metric-num {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--c-ink);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero__metric-label { color: var(--c-ink-3); line-height: 1.4; }

  .hero__actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--s-3); }
  .hero__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--s-3);
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    font-family: var(--f-body);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .hero__cta svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .hero__cta--primary {
    background: var(--c-ink);
    color: var(--c-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-ink);
  }
  .hero__cta--primary:hover { background: var(--c-amber); border-color: var(--c-amber); }
  .hero__cta--ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--c-ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }
  .hero__cta--ghost:hover { border-color: var(--c-ink); }
</style>
